channel.title: Need help with a deltascape source- I've tried almost everything
channel.description:
Hey, i've been trying to change a few safe coords and make them wild zones.
However, i havn't coded in like 5 months, so i forgot how to do it. Then i researched it and followed the steps, but the didn't go with delta sources. So, If anyone could help me, how do you change safe places to wilderness places in Deltascape Sources.
-Dyde

item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

Delta doesnt use “safe” and “wild” zones like most servers, delta uses wild like runescape with levels. So that is the problem your having right there.
